data.description: The garage has been remodeled it is now a sitting area for guest. It has a laundry closet soon as you walk in to the left of the sitting area. What use to be the garage has been paved and brick.when you come through the side door there is another the leads to the kitchen area right after that is the living room there's a door to the right in there use to be the den now it's a bedroom. Stay straight ahead is the hallway leading to on the left of the hallway is a half bathroom and the master bedroom with a full bathroom. Now on the right of the hallway are two more bedrooms in front of you will be the linen closet. A beautiful home for a single family.
